# How to use RewriteEngine

## What is Rewrite Engine?
- Apacheのモジュールであるmod_rewriteを利用するときに使う宣言文です。

## How to use Rewrite Engine (mod_rewrite)
- httpd.confや.htaccessでRewriteEngine onと書いておくだけで使える。

## RewriteCond Option
- RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d // If the request is not for a valid directory
- RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f // If the request is not for a valid file
- RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-l // If the request is not for a valid link
https://murashun.jp/blog/20141229-01.html#chapter-31
